Dialogue: 9,0:17:31.61,0:17:36.70,SAO1,Kirito,0,0,0,,{Including the Army, around 30% of them should be in the Starting Town, so...}Tính thêm cả Quân đoàn thì khoảng 30% đang ở Thị trấn khởi đầu.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:36.70,0:17:38.57,SAO1,Kirito,0,0,0,,{Maybe a bit short of 2,000 people?}Khoảng 2000 người chăng?
Dialogue: 9,0:17:38.57,0:17:41.49,SAO1,Asuna,0,0,0,,{Considering that, isn't this place a little deserted?}Nếu là vậy thì không phải nơi này hơi vắng vẻ sao?
Dialogue: 9,0:17:41.49,0:17:42.91,SAO1,Kirito,0,0,0,,{You're right...}Em nói cũng có lý...
Dialogue: 9,0:17:45.50,0:17:47.37,SAO1,Lady,0,0,0,,{Return the children!}Xin hãy trả lại mấy đứa trẻ cho tôi!
Dialogue: 9,0:17:47.37,0:17:50.09,SAO1,Army,0,0,0,,{Oh, their babysitter showed up.}Ố, trông trẻ-san tới rồi kìa.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:50.09,0:17:52.05,SAO1,Army,0,0,0,,{Hello! We've been waiting for you!}Yo! Chúng tôi đợi cô lâu rồi đấy!
Dialogue: 9,0:17:52.80,0:17:54.76,SAO1,Lady,0,0,0,,{Please, return the children!}Làm ơn, hãy trả lại mấy đứa trẻ cho tôi!
Dialogue: 9,0:17:55.55,0:17:58.76,SAO1,Army,0,0,0,,{Can you not make it sound like we're the bad guys here?}Cô nói cứ như bọn tôi là kẻ xấu vậy.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:58.76,0:18:03.72,SAO1,Army,0,0,0,,{We were just showing these kids how things work around here.}Chúng tôi chỉ cho tụi nhóc thấy cách mọi thứ ở đây hoạt động thôi mà.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:03.72,0:18:06.64,SAO1,Army,0,0,0,,{This is also an important part of the Army's duty.}Đây cũng là một nhiệm vụ quan trọng của Quân đoàn.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:06.64,0:18:07.69,SAO1,Army,0,0,0,,{Exactly.}Đúng đúng.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:07.69,0:18:10.15,SAO1,Army,0,0,0,,{Citizens have a duty to pay taxes, after all.}Công dân thì cũng phải có nhiệm vụ đóng thuế chứ.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:13.28,0:18:14.86,SAO1,Lady,0,0,0,,Gin! Kain! Mina!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:14.86,0:18:16.40,SAO1,Lady,0,0,0,,{Are you there?!}Các con có ở đó không?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:18.36,0:18:19.82,SAO1,Mina,0,0,0,,Sasha-sensei!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:19.82,0:18:21.74,SAO1,Mina,0,0,0,,Sensei, {help us!}cứu tụi con với!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:21.74,0:18:25.33,SAO1,Mina,0,0,0,,{Don't worry about the money, just hand it all over to them!}Cứ đưa tiền hết cho bọn họ đi.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:25.33,0:18:28.58,SAO1,Boy,0,0,0,,Sensei, {it won't be enough.}bọn con không đủ...
Dialogue: 9,0:18:29.04,0:18:33.00,SAO1,Army,0,0,0,,{You lot have built up quite a sum to pay off as it is.}Cô đã trốn một khoản thuế khá là lớn rồi đấy.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:33.00,0:18:35.67,SAO1,Army,0,0,0,,{We need you to give up your equipment as well,}Tốt hơn là cô nên cởi bỏ hết trang bị của mình ra,
Dialogue: 9,0:18:35.67,0:18:37.55,SAO1,Army,0,0,0,,{including all your armor.}kể cả áo giáp nữa. {shes not wearing armor '_'}
Dialogue: 9,0:18:37.55,0:18:40.05,SAO1,Army,0,0,0,,{Everything you have.}Tất cả những gì cô có.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:41.55,0:18:42.72,SAO1,Lady,0,0,0,,{Get...}Tránh...
Dialogue: 9,0:18:42.72,0:18:44.68,SAO1,Lady,0,0,0,,{Get out of my way!}Tránh xa tôi ra!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:44.68,0:18:45.56,SAO1,Lady,0,0,0,,{Or else...}Không thì...
Dialogue: 9,0:18:55.48,0:18:56.82,SAO1,Asuna,0,0,0,,{Everything's all right now.}Mọi chuyện ổn cả rồi.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.36,SAO1,Asuna,0,0,0,,{Take back your equipment.}Lấy lại trang bị của các em đi.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:01.37,0:19:02.41,SAO1,Army,0,0,0,,{Hey.}Này.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:02.41,0:19:03.58,SAO1,Army,0,0,0,,{What the hell?}Làm cái nồi gì thế?
Dialogue: 9,0:19:03.58,0:19:05.37,SAO1,Army,0,0,0,,{Who the heck are you guys?}Hai đứa bay là ai?
Dialogue: 9,0:19:05.99,0:19:09.04,SAO1,Army,0,0,0,,{Are you going to obstruct the duties of us, soldiers of the Army?!}Các người định cản trở công việc của Quân đoàn sao?!
Dialogue: 9,0:19:09.04,0:19:11.08,SAO1,Army,0,0,0,,{Whatever, give me a second.}Khoan, đợi chút đã.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:11.67,0:19:14.46,SAO1,Army,0,0,0,,{I haven't seen you two around these parts, but...}Ta chưa thấy bọn bay quanh đây, nhưng...
Dialogue: 9,0:19:14.46,0:19:18.22,SAO1,Army,0,0,0,,{you do know what it means to obstruct the Liberation Army, don't you?!} Chắc các người cũng biết chống lại Quân đoàn thì sẽ ra sao rồi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 9,0:19:21.59,0:19:24.30,SAO1,Asuna,0,0,0,,Kirito-kun, {take care of Yui-chan.}anh trông chừng Yui-chan dùm em.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:24.30,0:19:25.35,SAO1,Kirito,0,0,0,,{Right.}Ờ.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:48.66,0:19:50.16,SAO1,Asuna,0,0,0,,{Don't worry.}Đừng lo lắng.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:50.16,0:19:54.08,SAO1,Asuna,0,0,0,,{In a safe zone, no matter what happens, your HP won't drop.}Ở đây là khu vực an toàn, HP của anh không giảm xuống được đâu.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:54.08,0:19:58.46,SAO1,Asuna,0,0,0,,{Yes, there's only a light knockback effect.}Đúng rồi, đây chỉ là một hiệu ứng ngã bình thường thôi.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:58.46,0:20:02.43,SAO1,Asuna,0,0,0,,{But regardless, fights in safe zones can carve fear into people.}Chắc các người cũng biết những cuộc so đấu trong khu vực an toàn đáng sợ thế nào rồi chứ.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:04.18,0:20:05.76,SAO1,Army,0,0,0,,{S-Stop it!}Dừng lại!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:09.18,0:20:12.56,SAO1,Army,0,0,0,,{M-Men! Don't just stand there. Do something!}Mấy thằng kia! Đứng đó làm gì. Làm gì đi chứ!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:38.34,0:20:39.96,SAO1,Boy,0,0,0,,{Whoa.}Tuyệt quá!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:39.96,0:20:41.42,SAO1,Boy,0,0,0,,{That was amazing, Miss!}Tuyệt thật đấy, Onee-chan!{reminds me of shining bread}
Dialogue: 9,0:20:42.72,0:20:44.18,SAO1,Boy,0,0,0,,{I've never seen anything like it!}Em chưa từng thấy thứ gì như vậy hết!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:44.18,0:20:47.05,SAO1,Mina,0,0,0,,{Yeah, you were so cool!}Ừm, chị ngầu quá à!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:47.05,0:20:49.06,SAO1,Lady,0,0,0,,{Thank you very much.}Cám ơn em nhiều lắm.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:49.06,0:20:51.98,SAO1,Boy,0,0,0,,{You're the coolest! Thank you!}Chị là tuyệt nhất! Cám ơn chị!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.02,SAO1,Boy,0,0,0,,{I wish I could do that too!}Em ước gì mình có thể làm như thế!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:53.02,0:20:56.86,SAO1,Kirito,0,0,0,,{Well? Mama's super strong, right?}Thế nào? Mama mạnh lắm phải không?
Dialogue: 9,0:21:01.23,0:21:02.69,SAO1,Yui,0,0,0,,{Everyone's...}Mọi người...
Dialogue: 9,0:21:04.07,0:21:06.57,SAO1,Yui,0,0,0,,{Everyone's hearts...}Trái tim của mọi người...
Dialogue: 9,0:21:07.12,0:21:08.12,SAO1,Kirito,0,0,0,,Yui?
Dialogue: 9,0:21:08.70,0:21:09.83,SAO1,Asuna,0,0,0,,Yui-chan?
Dialogue: 9,0:21:10.41,0:21:13.16,SAO1,Kirito,0,0,0,,Yui, {what's wrong?}con sao thế?
Dialogue: 9,0:21:10.41,0:21:13.16,SAO2,Yui,0,0,0,,{Everyone's hearts...}Trái tim của mọi người...
Dialogue: 9,0:21:13.16,0:21:14.29,SAO1,Kirito,0,0,0,,Yui?
Dialogue: 9,0:21:14.29,0:21:18.00,SAO1,Asuna,0,0,0,,Yui-chan, {did you remember something?}con nhớ ra điều gì sao?
Dialogue: 9,0:21:18.00,0:21:20.75,SAO1,Yui,0,0,0,,{I... I...}Con... Con...
Dialogue: 9,0:21:20.75,0:21:25.34,SAO1,Yui,0,0,0,,{I wasn't here...}Con chưa từng ở đây...
Dialogue: 9,0:21:25.34,0:21:28.93,SAO1,Yui,0,0,0,,{I was always alone, in a dark place...}Con đã luôn cô đơn, con đã luôn ở trong bóng tối...
Dialogue: 9,0:21:40.94,0:21:42.07,SAO1,Kirito,0,0,0,,Yui!
Dialogue: 9,0:21:45.20,0:21:46.49,SAO1,Yui,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 9,0:21:46.49,0:21:48.82,SAO1,Yui,0,0,0,,{I'm scared, Mama...}Con sợ quá, Mama...
Dialogue: 9,0:21:50.37,0:21:53.16,SAO1,Kirito,0,0,0,,{What... was that?}Chuyện gì... vừa xảy ra vậy?
